9 THAT May 11 through May 17, 2025, is hereby recognized by the
10 Oklahoma House of Representatives as "National Police Week" and
11 recognizes May 15, 2025, as "Peace Officers Memorial Day" in
12 Oklahoma.
13 THAT the Oklahoma House of Representatives expresses condolences
14 to the loved ones of each law enforcement officer who has made the
15 ultimate sacrifice in the line of duty.
